A selection of stunning apartments located in the sought after location of SW3. Pelham Court offers residents many features associated with a Chelsea lifestyle, including an on-site porter and private communal gardens for sole use of the tenants. The apartments are set over 5 floors and are accessed via a lift. The flats can be rented on flexible terms either furnished or unfurnished.
